319.4	Ray_Kurzweil	Ray Kurzweil	Raymond "Ray" Kurzweil is an American author, scientist, inventor and futurist. Aside from futurology, he is involved in fields such as optical character recognition (OCR), text-to-speech synthesis, speech recognition technology, and electronic keyboard instruments. He is the author of several books on health, artificial intelligence (AI), transhumanism, the technological singularity, and futurism.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f4/Raymond_Kurzweil_Fantastic_Voyage.jpg/250px-Raymond_Kurzweil_Fantastic_Voyage.jpg
